  "2026-07-14T00:09:46.145Z",codex-gpt5,"Implementation evidence: added mutation-free getItemAt/readHistory APIs and pm get --at version-or-timestamp projection with restore-shared verified replay, structured valid-range errors, flag conflict rules, and immutable-history proof. Exact-tree strict gates pass; full sandboxed coverage passes 5656 tests at 100/100/100/100."
  "2026-07-14T00:29:10.047Z",codex-root,"Final verification: packed install reconstructs version 1 through CLI and SDK while the history hash remains unchanged; post-read SDK dry-run and real compaction verify; full coverage is 5656/5656 at 100/100/100/100 and package-first dogfood passes."
  "2026-07-14T00:45:19.141Z",codex-root,"Greptile review e72e80d9-93c1-4a1b-93cb-0f4799552240 found two shared-kernel regressions: restore errors lost command-specific wording, and future-adjacent timestamps no longer select the latest prior entry. Reopened for compatibility fixes and focused regressions."
  "2026-07-14T01:01:48.964Z",codex-root,"Review-fix evidence: shared resolveHistoryTarget now accepts explicit caller policy. pm get --at remains strict for future timestamps; restore preserves latest-entry-at-or-before behavior and restore-specific error wording. Linked 101-test focused matrix passed, full sandboxed coverage passed 5656/5656 at 100/100/100/100, and static quality/docstring/package/token gates are green."
  "2026-07-14T01:34:30.788Z",codex-root,"Hosted Greptile review on PR #549 at dd43d2e5 found a P1 acceptance regression: pm get --at still calls recordContextUsageTouches and mutates the derived context-usage ledger. Reopened to skip all usage-ledger writes for historical reads and add explicit immutability coverage."
  "2026-07-14T01:40:19.028Z",codex-root,"Hosted review fix verified: reconstructed pm get --at no longer calls recordContextUsageTouches. The focused test snapshots runtime/context-usage.jsonl before the historical read, proves it remains byte-identical, then proves a current read still appends usage feedback. Linked 101-test matrix passed; full coverage passed 5656/5656 at 100/100/100/100; ESLint and strict static/docstring/package/token gates passed."
  "2026-07-14T06:42:35.965Z",codex-root,"Exact-head review finding: Greptile thread 3575841761 proves pm get <id> --at <target> --fields children validates the projection but omits it because historical reads disable workspace child scans. Fixing the canonical immutable-read owner to reject this unsupported combination explicitly before rendering."
  "2026-07-14T06:44:41.687Z",codex-root,"Review remediation evidence: explicitly requested historical children projections now fail with EXIT_CODE.USAGE and a precise workspace-history indexing diagnostic instead of succeeding with an omitted field. Focused history/get matrix passes 102 tests; ESLint and strict 100% docstring/static gates pass; full sandboxed coverage completed successfully at 100/100/100/100."
  "2026-07-14T06:46:35.673Z",codex-root,"Packed-tarball manual acceptance: installed unbrained-pm-cli-2026.7.13.tgz into fresh /tmp/pm-cli-history-consumer-jrhObK, initialized a tracker, created and updated an Epic, verified get --at 1 returns reconstructed version 1, and verified --fields id,children exits 2 with the explicit unsupported historical relationship diagnostic."
